<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 15.6pt 0cm 0cm; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;">为深入学习贯彻习近平总书记关于教育工作的重要论述，弘扬教育家精神，切实增强教师“为党育人、为国育才”的责任感和使命感，持续推进教师队伍建设，1月19日，我校特邀请刘红宁教授对全体教职工进行了《弘扬教育家精神，奋勇争当新时代“大先生”》的专题讲座。讲座由校党委书记、督导专员江延湖主持。</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 15.6pt 0cm 0cm; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28pt; text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 15.6pt 0cm 0cm; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28pt;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;"><img src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/img/2024-01-22%2017%3A16%3A24%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%8711.jpg?Expires=2021274984&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&Signature=9OoTX%2BJEiFtL7%2Fbsol4qAIV7GE4%3D" alt="" width="650" height="432" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; filter: saturate(1.1); display: block;"/></span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 15.6pt 0cm 0cm; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28pt; text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;">讲座现场，刘教授先细致解读了《党的二十大精神》《习近平总书记关于教育的重要论述》《关于以教育家为榜样、大力弘扬教育家精神的重要指示精神》《习近平总书记向全国优秀教师代表致信精神的专题学习》等文件，他结合学校办学实际，从“理解教育家精神核心要义”“大力弘扬教育家精神，为强国建设民族复兴伟业作出新的更大贡献”两个方面具体阐释了教育家精神的深刻内涵和践行路径。</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28pt; text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28pt;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;"><img src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/img/2024-01-22%2017%3A17%3A04%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%8710.jpg?Expires=2021275024&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&Signature=5x9o1YIczHQw0%2B8A0SXm0iNuBHk%3D" alt="" width="650" height="433" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; filter: saturate(1.1); display: block;"/></span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28pt; text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;">回顾自己从教40多年的教书育人经历，他鼓励全体教师不仅要把所教的学科专业知识学精学深，更要成为能够勇挑新课程改革重任、能够重组课程的设计师，要不停地阅读、思考、实践、写作，不断创新教育思想理念和方式方法。坚持把加强自身修养作为一门终身的“必修课”，自觉坚守精神家园、坚守人格底线，带头践行社会主义核心价值观，以自己的模范行动影响和带动学生。</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28pt; text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28pt;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;"><img src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/img/2024-01-22%2017%3A17%3A30%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%8712.jpg?Expires=2021275050&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&Signature=e%2FkZ9ySlBUdnY77881iEgOop1Ro%3D" alt="" width="650" height="432" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; filter: saturate(1.1); display: block;"/></span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28pt; text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;">江延湖在主持时强调，全体教职工要以刘红宁教授及广大优秀教育家为榜样标杆，将弘扬教育家精神与学习贯彻党的二十大精神、习近平总书记考察江西重要讲话精神和习近平总书记关于教育的重要论述结合起来，树立“躬耕教坛、强国有我”的志向和抱负，自觉做“四有”好老师，新时代的“大先生”，为培养更多可堪大用、能担重任的时代新人，贡献智慧和力量！</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;">聆听刘教授的讲座，是一次思想的升华，更是一次心灵的洗礼。全体教职工深感使命光荣、责任重大，纷纷表示要牢记为党育人、为国育才的宗旨，深入领悟教育家精神的内涵，切实将其贯彻到日常工作中。</span></p><p><br/></p>